// go.work ties the three TeamChat modules into a single development workspace.
//
// With this file present, `go build ./...` from the repo root resolves
// teamchat/shared to the local ./shared directory for both services — no need
// to publish or version-tag the shared module during development.
//
// To build a single service for deployment (as if it were its own repo), cd
// into its directory; the replace directive in each service go.mod keeps the
// local resolution working outside the workspace too.
go 1.19

use (
	./shared
	./services/api-server
	./services/ws-worker
)
